widgets.title: System_Calls_Active
widgets.description:
Formula: %sess-curactcall%
Description: System - Total Active Sessions

widgets.title: Uplink Throughput Mbps
widgets.description:
Formula: ( 8 * %sess-rxbytes% / (Interval*60) /100000)
Description: System - Uplink Throughput in Mbps

widgets.title: SYSTEM_Throughput_Mbps
widgets.description:
Formula: ((8*(%sess-txbytes%+%sess-rxbytes%))/(INTERVAL*60)/1000/1000)
Description: System Throughput (Mbps)

widgets.title: Session_Manager_Max_CPU
widgets.description:
Formula: (%task-sessmgr-maxcpu%)
Description: Session Manager Max CPU (%)

widgets.title: Aggregate_CPU_Utilization_New
widgets.description:
Formula: (%cpubusy%/%numcpu%)
Description: Aggregate CPU Utilization New

widgets.title: CPU_Memory_Usage_Aggregate_new
widgets.description:
Formula: ((%memused%)/(%memtotal%) * 100)
Description: CPU Memory Usage Aggregate New

widgets.title: Session_Manager_Average_Memory_Utilization
widgets.description:
Formula: (%task-sessmgr-avgmem%)
Description: Session Manager Average Memory Utilization

widgets.title: Port_Utilization_Downlink
widgets.description:
Formula: (((%util-rx-curr% * 1000000) / (%maxrate%)) * 100)
Description: Port Utilization - Rx (%)

widgets.title: Port_Utilization_Uplink
widgets.description:
Formula: (((%util-tx-curr% * 1000000) / (%maxrate%)) * 100)
Description: Port Utilization -Tx (%)

widgets.title: IP_Pool_Utilization
widgets.description:
Formula: (100*(%used%)/(%used%+%free%+%hold%))
Description: IP Pool utilization

widgets.title: APN_Throughput_Gbps
widgets.description:
Formula: ((8*(%uplnk-bytes%+%dnlnk-bytes%))/(INTERVAL*60)/1000/1000/1000)
Description: APN Throughput (Gbps)

widgets.title: APN_Throughput_QCI1_Mbps
widgets.description:
Formula: ((8*(%qci1-uplinkbyte-fwd%+%qci1-dwlinkbyte-fwd%))/(INTERVAL*60)/1000/1000)
Description: APN Throughput QCI-1 (Mbps)

widgets.title: APN_Throughput_QCI5_Mbps
widgets.description:
Formula: ((8*(%qci5-uplinkbyte-fwd%+%qci5-dwlinkbyte-fwd%))/(INTERVAL*60)/1000/1000)
Description: APN Throughput QCI-5 (Mbps)

widgets.title: APN_Throughput_QCI8_Mbps
widgets.description:
Formula: ((8*(%qci8-uplinkbyte-fwd%+%qci8-dwlinkbyte-fwd%))/(INTERVAL*60)/1000/1000)
Description: APN Throughput QCI-8 (Mbps)

widgets.title: APN_Current_Number_of_Sessions
widgets.description:
Formula: (%sess-curr%)
Description: APN Current  Sessions

widgets.title: Gy_Transaction_Rate_Per_Second_New
widgets.description:
Formula: ((%cc-msg-ccrinit%+%cc-msg-ccrfinal%+%cc-msg-ccrupdate%+%cc-msg-raa%)/(INTERVAL*60))
Description: Gy TPS - New

widgets.title: Create_Session_Request_Success_Rate
widgets.description:

Description: Create Session Request Success Rate

widgets.title: EGTPC_Bearer_Update_Success_Rate

widgets.title: Gy_Credit_Control_Update_Success_Rate_AF
widgets.description:
Formula: (100 * ((%dpca-msg-ccaupd% - %dpca-msg-ccaupderror%) / %dpca-msg-ccrupd%) )
Description: Gx Credit Control Update Success Rate

widgets.title: IMSA_Credit_control_Update_Success_Rate
widgets.description:
Formula: (100 * ((%dpca-msg-ccaupd% - %dpca-msg-ccaupderror%) / %dpca-msg-ccrupd%) )
Description: Gx Credit Control Update Success Rate

widgets.title: Gx_RAR_Success_Rate
widgets.description:
